OL,3,CGranada Debate: Is it time for a
OL,4,Cvoting system change?
OL,6,FA former Conservative MP who lost his
OL,7,Fseat in the general election says it
OL,8,Fis time to change the voting system.
OL,10,FNigel Evans lost his seat in the
OL,11,FRibble Valley constituency of
OL,12,FLancashire, after serving parliament
OL,13,Ffor 32 years.
