OL,3,CGranada Debate: Is it time for a
OL,4,Cvoting system change?
OL,6,FReferring to the failed Alternative
OL,7,FVote referendum in 2011 he said: "We
OL,8,Fdid have a referendum which was
OL,9,Frejected by the public but that was
OL,10,Fjust one form of proportional
OL,11,Frepresentation.
OL,13,F"I think we do need, we have time, I
OL,14,Fdon't think Keir has an incentive to
OL,15,Fchange the voting system tomorrow but
OL,16,Flet's just have a look at what
OL,17,Fvariants are there."
