OL,3,CGranada Debate: Is it time for a
OL,4,Cvoting system change?
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MP Tom Morrison,
OL,7,Fwhose party has regularly campaigned
OL,8,Ffor a proportional style voting
OL,9,Fsystem, said they would use the new
OL,10,Fparliament term to push for reform.
OL,12,FThe Cheadle representative said: "The
OL,13,FLib Dems have been campaigning for
OL,14,Fvoter reform since day one in our
OL,15,Fparty's history," he said.
