OL,3,CGranada Debate: Is it time for a
OL,4,Cvoting system change?
OL,6,F"It's fair to say the first past the
OL,7,Fpost system is intrinsically unfair,
OL,8,Fit over represents the two main
OL,9,Fparties and we would do everything we
OL,10,Fcan in this parliament to make sure
OL,11,Fthat we get voter reform and change
OL,12,Fthat first past the post system.
OL,14,F"We are the biggest third party in the
OL,15,Flast century, I think we have the
OL,16,Fpower to put pressure on the labour
OL,17,Fgovernment to implement that change."
OL,19,FThe Liberal Democrats won 72 MPs in
OL,20,Fthe General Election, compared to
OL,21,FReform's five.
