OL,3,CGranada Debate: Is it time for a
OL,4,Cvoting system change?
OL,6,FMr Morrison added: "I think the key
OL,7,Fthing is, first past the post does not
OL,8,Fhelp represent the views of this
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,F"There are still too many safe seats
OL,12,Fwhich dictate where the parties get
OL,13,Ftheir power.
OL,15,F"There are only a few bellwether seats
OL,16,Fwhich can actually change a government
OL,17,Fand that's simply not fair, and if we
OL,18,Fneed to change that, and if it talks
OL,19,Fme out of a job but it gives people a
OL,20,Fproper democratic choice that's
OL,21,Fperfectly ok with me."
